Custom datasets will be stored here for model training

ground-truth
- Was intitially setup for testing the HOTA Metric on the track_eval.py code, however this has not been fully implemented yet

raw-images
- Contains the extracted images that can be annotated (Use extract_frames_for_annotating) Once, annotated the annotations.xml¨
can be exported from CVAT.

training_ready
- Contains the prepared dataset for yolo/coco formatted models. They are sorted in non_augmented and augmented dataset.

  - non_augmented datasets can be created using the cvat_to_yolo_coco.py, which will convert the images and annotation.xml
  from a raw-images folder

  - augmented datasets can be created using the augment_dataset, which will convert